<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,863,1191]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,478,1015,1041]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">General distribution:</emphasis>
Mainly southern in distribution from Pennsylvania south to Florida, west to Louisiana and Texas in the south and Ohio, Missouri, and Illinois in the Midwest. This species also occurs in the Neotropical Region from 
<collectingCountry box="[496,586,1090,1116]" name="Mexico" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Mexico</collectingCountry>
to 
<collectingCountry box="[623,699,1090,1116]" name="Brazil" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
